  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p855214/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/30/78bee2b6a6b2a7a8b291ab9d49ce11b5.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Cambodia&mdash;The P&rsquo;chum Ben At The&nbsp;</strong><strong><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Pagoda\" target=\"_blank\">Pagoda</a></strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">柬埔寨&mdash;&mdash;佛塔里的&ldquo;亡人节&rdquo;</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">In the tenth month of the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lunar\" target=\"_blank\">lunar</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/calendar\" target=\"_blank\">calendar</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">, which usually falls in September, Cambodian Buddhists celebrate the Pak Ben, 14 days during which they will wake before dawn each morning to prepare offerings of food and other gifts to the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/monk\" target=\"_blank\">monks</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;living in the local pagoda and to their ancestors.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">在佛历十月，通常是公历9月份，柬埔寨的佛教徒会庆祝&ldquo;亡人节&rdquo;，在这14天中他们每天天亮之前就起床准备食物和其他礼品用作祭品供奉祖先，并分发给住在当地寺庙里的僧人们。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/30/d69e93e9e7df6d47c516b5da45404ad7.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">On the 15th day villagers visit the pagoda with offerings of sweet&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sticky\" target=\"_blank\">sticky</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;rice and bean treats&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/wrap\" target=\"_blank\">wrapped</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;in banana leaves and other special foods to mark close of the Pak Ben.10月15这一天村民会用香蕉叶包着甜糯米饭和豆子还有其他特殊食物一起送到寺庙，&ldquo;亡人节&rdquo;仪式到此结束。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/30/35133491b20c067606581e0bb2a13bc6.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The P&rsquo;chum Ben festival is a day when people wear their&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fine\" target=\"_blank\">finest</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;clothes, get together with family and friends at the local pagoda, and listen to monks.在&ldquo;亡人节&rdquo;这一天人们都穿上最华丽的服装，和家人朋友聚集在当地寺庙，听僧侣诵经。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p855214/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p855214\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p854261/\">备战CET6口语：自我介绍篇</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p819221/\">BBC榜单：世界最伟大10家博物馆 | 双语有声</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p838899/\">4个现象暗示你，该离开了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p839675/\">双语美文：多一份谅解，自己的生活也会更好</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p878193/\">Quora精选：为什么我无法长时间学习？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p878267/\">杭州包子美国开分店 20元一个在哈佛卖疯了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857798/\">今秋最值得学的10门英语课程</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749886/\">英语四级听力：超准！听力5大原则</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725820/\">爱上新概念英语的正确方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p882062/\">备考六级：30天背完六级高频词组（十三）</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
